# =====================================================================
# 22a_abstain_margin_validation_v2.R — Validate keeping δ abstain OFF (M04, v2)
#   Purpose:
#     - Using v2 artifacts, prove whether δ=0 (no abstain margin) is optimal
#       for the selected M04 operating point objective.
#   Method:
#     - Fix p* for M04 (from v2_operating_points.csv if available; else recompute
#       from v2_model04_threshold_sweep.csv via coverage × top-1 on validation,
#       tie -> lower threshold).
#     - Sweep δ in [0, 0.50] by 0.01. Cover a play when:
#          (max_p ≥ p*) AND (max_p − second_p ≥ δ).
#     - For each δ compute on validation and test:
#          coverage, top1_on_cov, expected_correct = coverage × top1_on_cov, mrr_on_cov.
#     - Decide: if best δ on validation is 0 (or within ε of best), we recommend keeping δ OFF.
#
# Inputs:
#   - artifacts/v2_model04_threshold_sweep.csv   (from Script 21)
#   - artifacts/v2_model04_val_preds_cal.csv     (preferred) OR
#     artifacts/v2_model04_val_preds.csv with column p_cal
#   - artifacts/v2_model04_test_preds_cal.csv    (preferred) OR
#     artifacts/v2_model04_test_preds.csv with column p_cal
#   - Optional: artifacts/v2_operating_points.csv (from Script 22) to read M04 p*
#
# Outputs:
#   - artifacts/v2_m04_delta_sweep_val.csv
#   - artifacts/v2_m04_delta_sweep_test.csv
#   - artifacts/v2_m04_delta_summary.csv
#   - artifacts/v2_m04_delta_report.md
#   - artifacts/v2_m04_delta_status.csv
#   - artifacts/v2_m04_delta_status.md
# =====================================================================

